<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink357">
<l>kurava malara maravam pūppac</l>
<l>curaṉaṇi koṇṭa kāṉaṅ kāṇūu</l>
<l>vaḻuṅkuka ceyporuṭ celaveṉa virumpiniṉ</l>
<l>ṉaṅkaliḻ māmai kaviṉa</l>
<l>vantaṉar tōḻinaṅ kāta lōrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>My friend! Our lover has come back, </l>
<l>desiring your dark beauties, shining with loveliness, </l>
<l>saying: “Damned be going for wealth that has to be made!” </l>
<l>after seeing the forest taking adornment of the desert, </l>
<l>when Kurava tree blossomed and Kadamba tree bloomed. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
